{dupe}'s recent conversation with another Duplicant shows a correlation to improved serotonin and <link=\"MORALE\">Morale</link> levels in this Duplicant. It is very possible that small talk with a co-worker, however short and seemingly insignificant, will make my Duplicant's feel connected to the colony as a whole.\n\nAs the colony gets bigger and more sophisticated, I must ensure that the opportunity for such connections continue, for the good of my Duplicants' mental well being.